nodes.text: An unidentified Aqualish technician served the Confederacy of Independent Systems on Skytop Station.

In 22 BBY, this Aqualish technician was working on a bank of equipment in Skytop Station when Count Dooku and Asajj Ventress toured the newly completed  listening post. Later that year, following the Battle of Bothawui, R2-D2 was brought to the station by Trandoshan scavenger Gha Nachkt. The tech attempted to block his work station screen from the prying sensors of the astromech droid. He helped Grievous to defend the station when the Jedi attacked it and died when the station was destroyed.
